wood.name: LIVE EDGE WOOD SLABS, ROUNDS, OVALS FOR SALE
wood.description: www.arborupcycle.comLIVE EDGE WOOD SLABS FOR SALE, ROUNDS, OVALS, AND MORE.FREE WOOD SCRAPS always available!Products :- Live Edge Slabs (wet, dried)- Various wood pieces and tree parts (incl. stumps, branches, etc.)Services :- Custom milling (including dimensional lumber milling)- Log/reclaimed wood hauling- Planing and Surfacing (Free scrap wood available at the warehouse from 9-2 daily M-F (only during these hours).  Pieces perfect for small woodworkers or people who want to take their try with wood. Grab it for free.)Arbor Upcycle is the only company in San Francisco dedicated to salvaging and milling downed trees in San Francisco. After a tree is removed due to storm damage or urban development Arbor Upcycle will strive to salvage the tree for its timber. The tree is then milled into slabs on-site or at our warehouse. The 3” wood slabs are then stickered and set aside to cure until they are stable enough to build with or sell.Every piece is identified by its true species and neighborhood in San Francisco where the tree once stood.Arbor Upcycle is not only salvaging valuable timber and sequestering carbon off-gassing but also reclaiming some of San Francisco’s oldest residing residents and in doing so is preserving SF’s heritage in the face of a rapidly changing urban landscape.Next time you need a tree removed or see a tree being removed we hope you think of Arbor Upcycle and our mission to sustainably manage our urban forest and contribute to our community.    http://arborupcycle.com/

Original finish but does show slight wear, but very nice for it’s age. No dents & the serial numbers do match, and the original case is in very good condition. Please email with any questions.

famous.name: Lots of Piano Sheet Music
famous.description: ***LOCATED IN DISCOVERY BAY***I don't check email much. Please call or text if interested.I have lots of ads up. Please click more ads by this user to see them all.We acquired all this music and books from an estate.  I have boxes of sheet music and whole books of music, mainly for vocals.  Old music, really old music.  I don't have anything current.  Lots of classical and holiday.  There are books of opera, composers and more.  I also have a few books about famous composers.  Much of the music has copyrights prior to 1950.  Some as old as the late 1800's.  The owner was German.  Have some German music.These start from $.50 to a few dollars a book.  Look through and take what you want.  Make an offer on the lot.Please call or text for quicker service.
